Gladys Kingsbury https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gladys_Kingsbury 0 Gladys Kingsbury (July 30, 1876 – November 10, 1958) was an American silent film actress and screenwriter mainly known for her role in Her Younger Sister (1914). She was married to Frank Cooley.
